HEADWORD: Infanta
<hw>In*fan"ta</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sp. & Pg., fem.
of <ets>infante</ets>. See <er>Infante</er>.]</ety> <def>A title borne
by every one of the daughters of the kings of Spain and Portugal, except
the eldest.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

